Regulatory compliance and risk management are also driving factors for NLP adoption in industries such as healthcare and BFSI. NLP technologies play a crucial role in analyzing textual data to identify compliance issues, mitigate risks, and improve decision-making processes. The expansion of e-commerce and digital marketing activities further fuels the demand for NLP tools that can enhance content analysis, sentiment tracking, and customer segmentation, providing actionable insights to optimize marketing strategies and improve brand perception.

